							<li><strong>Electrical hazards:</strong> Fence contact with power lines or electrical equipment</li>
							<li><strong>Sharp debris:</strong> Broken fence creating injury risks for people or pets</li>
							<li><strong>Structural collapse:</strong> Large sections that could fall and cause injury</li>
						</ul>

						<h3>Security Compromises</h3>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>Complete barrier failure:</strong> Fence down along property perimeter</li>
							<li><strong>Gate malfunction:</strong> Security gates that won't close or lock</li>
							<li><strong>Large openings:</strong> Gaps allowing unauthorized access</li>
							<li><strong>Pool fence damage:</strong> Safety barriers around swimming pools compromised</li>
						</ul>

