						<h3>Ensure Safety First</h3>
						<p>Before addressing fence damage, prioritize safety:</p>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>Clear the area:</strong> Keep people and pets away from damaged sections</li>
							<li><strong>Check for electrical hazards:</strong> Look for power lines or electrical contact</li>
							<li><strong>Assess structural stability:</strong> Determine if remaining sections are stable</li>
							<li><strong>Call emergency services:</strong> Contact 911 if there are immediate safety risks</li>
						</ul>

						<h3>Document the Situation</h3>
